cs.CV, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.CR, cs.MM 

This paper is about visual recognition systems and their training using obfuscated images. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.CV (Computer Vision and Pattern Recognition). The paper also discusses machine learning techniques for training recognition models, which suggests that it could also belong to cs.LG (Machine Learning). Additionally, the paper addresses privacy concerns, which could place it in cs.CR (Cryptography and Security). Finally, the paper uses several datasets, including CelebA and MTFL, which are related to multimedia and could place it in cs.MM (Multimedia).
